      <p class="visual-diagram__caption">
        A simplified decision tree for choosing between prompting, RAG, and
        fine-tuning. Real decisions often involve hybrid approaches,
        for example using RAG <em>and</em> fine-tuning together. The key
        factor is validation: if your current approach meets your threshold,
        added complexity is not justified. Illustrative diagram.
