      <li><a href="https://doi.org/10.1073/pnas.2305016120" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gilardi, Alizadeh &amp; Haunss (2023), <em>ChatGPT Outperforms Crowd-Workers for Text-Annotation Tasks</em></a>: landmark comparison of LLM and human annotation quality, with important caveats.</li>
      <li><a href="https://scikit-learn.org/stable/modules/model_evaluation.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Scikit-learn classification metrics</a>: Cohen&rsquo;s &kappa;, F1, precision, recall, and confusion matrix implementations.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Further reading:</strong></p>
    <ul class="resource-list">
      <li><a href="https://doi.org/10.1177/20531680241236579" target="_blank" rel="noopener">T&ouml;rnberg (2024), <em>ChatGPT-4 Outperforms Experts and Crowd Workers in Annotating Political Twitter Messages</em></a>: zero-shot LLM classification on political stance.</li>
